    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]

          ELSE N'OTRO'

          ELSE N'Sin asignar'

SELECT [a1].[CodCedula], [a1].[NombreCompleto], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[CodCedula], [a].[Celular], [a].[CodCargo], [a].[CodSucursal], [a].[EmpleadoEstado], [a].[FecVinculacion], [a].[Genero], [a].[NombreCompleto]
    FROM [AdmEmpleados] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[FecVinculacion] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN [AdmCargos] AS [a0] ON [a1].[CodCargo] = [a0].[CodCargo]
LEFT JOIN [AdmUnidades] AS [a2] ON [a0].[CodUnidad] = [a2].[CodUnidad]

SELECT [a1].[CodCedula], [a1].[NombreCompleto], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[CodCedula], [a].[Celular], [a].[CodCargo], [a].[CodSucursal], [a].[EmpleadoEstado], [a].[FecVinculacion], [a].[Genero], [a].[NombreCompleto]
    FROM [AdmEmpleados] AS [a]

    ORDER BY [a].[FecVinculacion] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]

ORDER BY [a1].[FecVinculacion] DESC

SELECT [a1].[CodCedula], [a1].[NombreCompleto], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[CodCedula], [a].[Celular], [a].[CodCargo], [a].[CodSucursal], [a].[EmpleadoEstado], [a].[FecVinculacion], [a].[Genero], [a].[NombreCompleto]
    FROM [AdmEmpleados] AS [a]
    WHERE LOWER([a].[NombreCompleto]) LIKE @__trimmedSearch_0_contains ESCAPE N'\'
    ORDER BY [a].[FecVinculacion] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN [AdmCargos] AS [a0] ON [a1].[CodCargo] = [a0].[CodCargo]
LEFT JOIN [AdmUnidades] AS [a2] ON [a0].[CodUnidad] = [a2].[CodUnidad]
LEFT JOIN [AdmSucursales] AS [a3] ON [a1].[CodSucursal] = [a3].[CodSucursal]
ORDER BY [a1].[FecVinculacion] DESC

          ELSE N'Sin asignar'
      END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE

    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[CodCedula], [a].[Celular], [a].[CodCargo], [a].[CodSucursal], [a].[EmpleadoEstado], [a].[FecVinculacion], [a].[Genero], [a].[NombreCompleto]

) AS [a1]

    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]

) AS [a1]

SELECT [a1].[CodCedula], [a1].[NombreCompleto], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[CodCedula], [a].[Celular], [a].[CodCargo], [a].[CodSucursal], [a].[EmpleadoEstado], [a].[FecVinculacion], [a].[Genero], [a].[NombreCompleto]
    FROM [AdmEmpleados] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[FecVinculacion] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN [AdmCargos] AS [a0] ON [a1].[CodCargo] = [a0].[CodCargo]
LEFT JOIN [AdmUnidades] AS [a2] ON [a0].[CodUnidad] = [a2].[CodUnidad]

ORDER BY [a1].[FecVinculacion] DESC

SELECT [a1].[CodCedula], [a1].[NombreCompleto], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[CodCedula], [a].[Celular], [a].[CodCargo], [a].[CodSucursal], [a].[EmpleadoEstado], [a].[FecVinculacion], [a].[Genero], [a].[NombreCompleto]
    FROM [AdmEmpleados] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[FecVinculacion] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN [AdmCargos] AS [a0] ON [a1].[CodCargo] = [a0].[CodCargo]
LEFT JOIN [AdmUnidades] AS [a2] ON [a0].[CodUnidad] = [a2].[CodUnidad]
LEFT JOIN [AdmSucursales] AS [a3] ON [a1].[CodSucursal] = [a3].[CodSucursal]
ORDER BY [a1].[FecVinculacion] DESC

    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]

    SELECT [a].[CodCedula], [a].[Celular], [a].[CodCargo], [a].[CodSucursal], [a].[EmpleadoEstado], [a].[FecVinculacion], [a].[Genero], [a].[NombreCompleto]
    FROM [AdmEmpleados] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[FecVinculacion] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]

LEFT JOIN [AdmUnidades] AS [a2] ON [a0].[CodUnidad] = [a2].[CodUnidad]

    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
    WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'
END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
    ELSE N'Sin asignar'
END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[CodCedula], [a].[Celular], [a].[CodCargo], [a].[CodSucursal], [a].[EmpleadoEstado], [a].[FecVinculacion], [a].[Genero], [a].[NombreCompleto]
    FROM [AdmEmpleados] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[FecVinculacion] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN [AdmCargos] AS [a0] ON [a1].[CodCargo] = [a0].[CodCargo]
LEFT JOIN [AdmUnidades] AS [a2] ON [a0].[CodUnidad] = [a2].[CodUnidad]

END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'

    WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]

    WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
    ELSE N'OTRO'

          WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL THEN [a0].[NombreCargo]
          ELSE N'Sin asignar'
      END AS [NombreCargo], CASE
          WHEN [a0].[CodCargo] IS NOT NULL AND [a2].[CodUnidad] IS NOT NULL THEN [a2].[NombreUnidad]
          ELSE N'Sin asignar'
      END AS [NombreUnidad], CASE
          WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'M' THEN N'MASCULINO'
          WHEN [a1].[Genero] = N'F' THEN N'FEMENINO'
          ELSE N'OTRO'
      END AS [Genero], [a1].[Celular], CASE
          WHEN [a3].[CodSucursal] IS NOT NULL THEN [a3].[NombreSucursal]
          ELSE N'Sin asignar'
      END AS [NombreSucursal], [a1].[FecVinculacion] AS [FechaVinculacion], CAST([a1].[EmpleadoEstado] AS int) AS [EmployeeStatus]

          ORDER BY [a].[FecVinculacion] DESC
          OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
      ) AS [a1]
      LEFT JOIN [AdmCargos] AS [a0] ON [a1].[CodCargo] = [a0].[CodCargo]
      LEFT JOIN [AdmUnidades] AS [a2] ON [a0].[CodUnidad] = [a2].[CodUnidad]

          (SELECT *
